704068f-a.title: Brooklyn: Eastern Parkway - Washington Avenue
704068f-a.text:
Eastern Parkway, at the S.W. corner of Eastern Parkway and Washington
Ave. This is a view of the Brooklyn Institute of Art and Sciences,
(also known as the 3rooklyn Museum).
About 1925.
Ewing Galloway.
